# Hugo production build output, kept here only as the URL-parity reference
# baseline for the Astro migration (see scripts/freeze-urls.mjs, url-manifest.json).
#
# Astro defaults public/ to its static source dir, but the only genuine source
# asset is images/cc.svg (already tracked — git never re-ignores tracked files).
# Everything else here is generated; ignore it all.
*
!.gitignore
